{"tid":1524701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫香港人加油，因為香港人都係","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T07:19:21.000Z","uid":81236,"like":545,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b9d6ef93f20a641ef45f16a3307eb12ba4c805","tid":1524701,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為到而家未有任何一個黑警、被人捉到既鬼或者周圍打人既藍絲受到制裁<br />\n<br />\n連人道救援既救護員都比人要面壁同埋閘開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到而家都仲係講香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連香港人反抗都唔敢講同做</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人咁都仲唔係垃圾係咩？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a62aeddd1f614c3d666396de5bf4c3f793b11b75","tid":1524701,"uid":81236,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"跟我一齊講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a88ebf1de41eff4a5a9257702cefa70afee9bbcb","tid":1524701,"uid":120040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<br />\n和理非出動嘅時候到了 你唔係忍到今日手足為你犧牲呀?"},{"pid":"d8dcfc4005d34ec99b45c7f1a51974146a91c63a","tid":1524701,"uid":22566,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"a62aeddd1f614c3d666396de5bf4c3f793b11b75","tid":1524701,"uid":81236,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"跟我一齊講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><sp